      "author": "jabaho9523",
      "description": "Initial release of Vault Plus — a vault health dashboard for Obsidian.\n\n**What it finds:**\n- Orphan notes (no incoming/outgoing links)\n- Broken links (missing targets)\n- Empty notes (no content or near-zero bytes)\n- Oversized notes (above word threshold)\n- Fuzzy duplicates (similar titles)\n- Unused tags (only in one note)\n- Unreferenced attachments (no note links to them)\n\nAll checks toggleable. One-click Open, Delete, and Open-both actions. Auto-rescan on vault changes. 100% offline.",
